(13, 'BTU-B48CD864', 5, 'Mrs.', 'Ayamdor', 'Aurelia Anongyorige', 'ayamdoraaurelia@gmail.com', '+233 540721397', NULL, 'Zorko', 'Zorko, Bolgatanga-Ghana', 'Upper East', 'Ghanaian', 'Christianity', 'single', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GHA-722767173-6', '2000-08-13', 'female', 'Master\'s Degree (Other)', 'Abdou Moumouni University, Niger', 1, 'Published a research article titled “Comparative Overview of Water Splitting and Biological Techniques of Hydrogen Production” in the International Journal of Sustainable and Green Energy, Volume 15, Issue 1 (DOI: 10.11648/j.ijsge.20261501.15).', 'My teaching experience is relevant to the post being applied for in the electrical and electronics department. Under this department is the renewable energy engineering. Introduction to Renewable Energy, Solar Photovoltaic Systems, Hydrogen Technologies, and Energy Economics, which directly match the subject areas of the post. This has equipped me with skills in delivering lectures and helping students to understand complex topics. In addition my research experience has strengthened my practical knowledge in the field of photovoltaics. his combination of teaching and research experience positions me to contribute meaningfully to curriculum development and student mentorship,', 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'Reading, Exploring new things', 'Immediately', 'No please', 'Prof. Ayouba Mahamane Abdoulkadri', 'Lecturer', 'Coordinator of IMP-EGH, WASCAL DRPCCE and Professor at Abdou Moumouni University', 'PO BOX: 10662, Niamey, Niger.', '+227 80 03 36 46', 'ayouba.a@wascal.org', 'Dr. Felix Amankwah Diawuo', 'Lecturer', 'Senior lecturer with the Department of Energy and Petroleum Engineering at the University of Energy ', 'P.O. Box 214,\r\nSunyani', '+233 205100539', NULL, 'Mr. Frank Adabre', 'Corporate leadership at NorthLite Solar Limited', 'CEO', 'Plot 57, Wateraid Avenue, Kumbosigo-Bolgatanga', '+233 244412150', NULL, 'BTU_B48CD864_cv_6a0eeb454627b5.75347874.pdf', 'Aurelia_Ayamdor_Documents.p