(20, 'BTU-4D4564C1', 8, 'Mr.', 'Ajuik', 'Awombadek Richard', 'ajuikrichard@yahoo.com', '0549778638', 'Bolgatanga Technical University, Post Office Box 767, Bolgatanga, UER- Ghana', 'Accra', 'Wiesi', 'Upper East', 'Ghana', 'Christianity', 'married', 'Mercy Asiatewen Amuntoate', 'Danbel Lodge, Sandema- UER- Ghana', 'Daniella A. Ajuik- 28/08/2011\r\nAnable A. Ajuik- 25/10/2015\r\nRichmond A. Ajuik 08/11/2018', 'P001742337', 'GH7161020041', '1979-03-28', 'male', 'PhD', 'University of Business and Integrated development Studies', 0, 'Reviewed and Accepted for Publication: Advanced International Journal for Research on Analyzing the Impact of Inflation on Economic Growth in Ghana.', 'As a Part- Time Assistant Lecturer with the Department of Accounting and Finance, i have already gained experience in teaching and research. Besides, my PhD in Business Administration in the field of Finance will further enhance my research and professional career in the academia.', 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'Watching Football', 'Immediate', 'I am an Entrepreneur engaged in the Business of Farming.', 'Dr. Fuseini Mahama', 'Lecturer', 'Head of Department- Accounting and Finance', 'Bolgatanga Technical University, Post Office Box 767, Bolgatanga, UER- Ghana', '0541437993', 'Fmahama@bolgatu.edu.gh', 'Prof. Joseph Abazaami', 'Lecturer', 'Deputy Director, Centre for Interdisciplinary Studies, UDS Tamale/ Council Member- UBIDS', 'University for Development Studies Post Office Box TL 1350, Tamale, Ghana.', '0200741220', 'abazaami@yahoo.com', 'Mr. Alexis Kwabena Asuinura', 'Accountant', 'Board Chairman, Builsa Community Bank Ltd', 'Builsa Community Bank Ltd, Post Office Box 25, Sandema, UER- Ghana', '0202016477', 'aalexis@yahoo.com', 'BTU_4D4564C1_cv_6a0f39756a8d47.78542929.pdf', 'MBA Finance.pdf', 'shortlisted', '', '154.161.121.163', '2026-05-21 16:57:25', '2026-06-13 00:05:25', 'BTU_4D4564C1_photo_6a0f39756a8db1.78749142.jpg', 'e820b8ce-1cf6-4761-bbc4-ed2089da3865.jpg');
