(35, 'BTU-071F6B4A', 2, 'Dr.', 'Bonya', 'Kwame', 'lopezkocha@gmail.com', '0554419318', 'Bolgatanga Senior High School\r\n     P. O. Box 176\r\n     Bolgatanga, U. E. R.\r\n     Ghana.', 'Berekum', 'Sunyani', 'Bono', 'Ghanaian', 'Christianity', 'single', NULL, NULL, 'Asare Boakye Dankwa - 10/12/2000', NULL, 'GHA-716236676-4', '1979-12-02', 'male', 'PhD', 'C. K, Tedam University of Technology and Applied Sciences', 11, 'i.   Bonya, K., Twum, S. B., &amp; Etwire, C. J. (2025). A Comparative Analysis of Multicriteria Decision Making (MCDM) Methods in Optimal Gold Mining Site Selection in Ghana. IOSR Journal of Mathematics (IOSR-JM), 2,2278–8727.\r\n\r\nii.  Bonya, K., Twum, S. B., &amp; Etwire, C. J (2025). A Revised TOPSIS with Weighted Euclidean Distances. IOSR Journal of Mathematics (IOSR-JM), 3, 2278 – 8727.', 'My strong academic background, comprising a BSc, MSc, and PhD in Mathematics, together with 20 years of teaching Elective Mathematics, demonstrates extensive subject knowledge, teaching competence, and experience in curriculum delivery and student assessment. My experience as a part-time lecturer at the KNUST–IDL centre in Bolgatanga has exposed me to tertiary education, academic mentoring, and learner support. At the same time, my postgraduate supervisory role reflects my research and academic guidance capabilities. Additionally, my experience as a regional sales executive enhanced my leadership, communication, and administrative skills, making me well-qualified for the position of Mathematics Lecturer at this noble institution.', 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'Watching movies,\r\n listening to music,\r\n Traveling.', 'Immediately', NULL, 'Prof. Stephen B. Twum', 'Lecturer', 'Lecturer', 'Department of Mathematics\r\nFaculty of Mathematical Sciences\r\nCKT - UTAS, Navrongo, U. E. R.\r\nGhana.', '0546332794,    02013', 'stwum@cktutas.edu.gh', 'Dr. Christian J. Etwire', 'Lecturer', 'Head of Department', 'Department of Mathematics\r\n Faculty of Mathematical Sciences\r\n CKT - UTAS., Navrongo, U. E. R.\r\nGhana.', '0246013140,    05091', 'cetwire@cktutas.edu.gh', 'Mr. Mukasa Zoogah', 'Northern Zone Coordinator, KNUST - IDL', 'Senior Assistant Registrar', 'KNUST - IDL Centre,\r\nNorthern Zone,\r\nTamale, Ghana.', '0244771773', 'esthermuk2007@yahoo.com', 'BTU_071F6B4A_cv_6a10348c8af934.20332573.pdf', 'CURICULUM VITAE.pdf', 'pending', NULL, '154.161.249.238', '2026-05-22 10:48:44', '2026-05-22 10:48:44', 'BTU_071F6B4A_photo_6a10348c8af9a3.48802385.jpg', 'PICTURE.jpg'),
(36, 'BTU-7C530B54', 10, 'Mr.', 'Ayamga', 'Michael Asakiyaaba', 'ayamgamichael2@gmail.com', '+233240126906', 'Bolgatanga Technical University, Box 176.', 'KANDIGA', 'Kandiga', 'Upper East', 'GHANAIAN', 'Catholic', 'married', 'Anyongo Alice Auligama', 'Bolgatanga Regional Hospital', NULL, NULL, 'GHA-715963336-7', '1987-04-24', 'male', 'Master\'s Degree (MPhil.)', 'C. K. T University of Technology and Applied Science', 11, 'An IoT-Based Water Leakage Detection and Localization System\r\nAsian Journal of Research in Computer Science', 'My publication titled “An IoT-Based Water Leakage Detection and Localization System” is relevant to the post because it demonstrates my expertise in IoT, embedded systems, programming, and intelligent monitoring technologies. The research involved the design and implementation of a smart leakage detection system using sensors and microcontrollers, which aligns with courses in Computing and Information Technology. It also reflects my ability to conduct practical, problem-solving research, supervise student projects, and contribute to innovation and academic development in the institution.', 'no', 'no', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Programming and Music', 'If appointed, I would be available to assume the appointment immediately upon notification or within', 'I wish to acknowledge that I have been a part-time lecturer at Bolgatanga Technical University in the department of Computing and Information Technology (CIT) since 2024', 'Dr. Calistus Napkhi', 'Lecturer', 'Senior Lecturer', '1.C.K. Tedam University of Technology and Applied Science', '0207389181', NULL, 'Prof Peter Agbedibab', 'College Principal', 'Principal', 'Tumu College of Education', '0208529740', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BTU_7C530B54_cv_6a10441b869a51.28679675.pdf', 'Application documents Ayamga Michael.pdf', 'shortlisted', '', '41.155.117.245', '2026-05-22 11:55:07', '2026-06-12 23:32:57', 'BTU_7C530B54_photo_6a10441b869ad4.97403330.jpg', 'Michael.jpg'),
