(42, 'BTU-D4C55F45', 1, 'Mr.', 'Aetdene', 'Azure Wilson', 'aetdene@protonmail.com', '+233245806509', 'Zuarungu Senior High School P.O.Box 133 Bolgatanga Ghana', 'Bolgatanga', 'Bolgatanga', 'Upper East', 'Ghana', 'Islam', 'married', 'Taufikatu zakariya', 'Zuarungu Senior High School P.O.Box 133', 'Azure Muhibatu- 18th November, 2014\r\nAzure Hafisatu- 1st January, 2018\r\nAzure  Emiran  - 7th December, 2021\r\nAzure Fawzan  22nd October,  2025\r\nAzure  Fawaz  22nd October, 2025', NULL, 'GHA-715427986-9', '1987-07-10', 'male', 'Master\'s Degree (MPhil.)', 'University for development studies', 7, '1. “EMHD Flow of Carbon-Based Nanofluids over a Plane Sheet with Rotations and Soret Effects.”\r\nPublished in the International Journal of Mathematical Modeling &amp; Computations, pp. 89–100.', 'My teaching, research, and professional experience align strongly with the requirements of a full-time lecturer position. \r\n\r\nI have teaching experience in Engineering Mathematics at Bolgatanga Technical University, where I teach HND and B.Tech students in areas such as calculus, differential equations, statistics, and applied mathematics.\r\n\r\n My MPhil in Mathematics from University for Development Studies and my research in fluid dynamics, numerical analysis, and nanofluid modeling have strengthened my analytical and research capabilities. In addition, I possess experience in student supervision, assessment preparation, academic mentoring, and the use of mathematical software such as MATLAB, Maple, and LaTeX, making me well-suited for effective teaching, research, and academic service.', 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'I enjoy watching football and playing Valley ball', 'Immediately', 'I am Currentlya final year  PhD Candidate at University of Technology and Applied science Navrongo.  Hopeful of graduating this year December.', 'Benjamin Apam', 'Quality Assurance', 'Head of quality assurance Bolgatanga technical university', 'P.O.BOX 767 UPPER EAST REGION GHANA', '+233 24 629 8163', 'bapam@bolgatu.edu.gh', 'Prof. Rabiu Musah', 'Senior lecturer', 'Head of department  School of engineering university of development studies', 'P.O.BOX TL 135O TAMALE GHANA', '+233 54 584 3562', 'mrabiu@uds.edu.gh', 'Engr. Norbert Johnson Amoanab', 'Lecturer', 'Head of mechanical engineering department', 'P.O.Box 767 Upper East Region Ghana', '+233 55 396 9133', 'namoanab@bolgatu.edu.gh', 'BTU_D4C55F45_cv_6a109803d105d4.02482696.pdf', 'Azure CV.pdf', 'pending', NULL, '41.204.44.18', '2026-05-22 17:53:07', '2026-06-07 23:59:41', 'BTU_D4C55F45_photo_6a109803d10637.31089911.jpg', 'Azure Aetidene passport.JPG'),
(43, 'BTU-C53AD233', 2, 'Mr.', 'Aetdene', 'Azure Wilson', 'aberezaaya@yahoo.com', '+233245806509', 'Zuarungu Senior High School P.O.Box 133 Bolgatanga-East Upper East Region,  Ghana', 'Bolgatanga', 'Tanzui', 'Upper East', 'Ghana', 'Islam', 'married', 'Taufikatu zakariya', 'House No F255 Tanzui Bolgatanga', 'Azure Muhibatu- 18th November 2014\r\nAzure Hafisatu  - 1st January 2018\r\nAzure Emiran  - 7th December 2021\r\nAzure Fawzan  - 22nd October 2025\r\nAzure  Fawaz  - 22nd October 2021', NULL, 'GHA-715427986-9', '1987-07-10', 'male', 'Master\'s Degree (MPhil.)', 'University for development studies', 5, '1.  “EMHD Flow of Carbon-Based Nanofluids over a Plane Sheet with Rotations and Soret Effects.”\r\nPublished in the International Journal of Mathematical Modeling &amp; Computations, pp. 89–100.', 'My teaching, research, and professional experience align strongly with the requirements of a full-time lecturer position. I have teaching experience in Engineering Mathematics at Bolgatanga Technical University, where I teach HND and B.Tech students in areas such as calculus, differential equations, statistics, and applied mathematics. My MPhil in Mathematics from University for Development Studies and my research in fluid dynamics, numerical analysis, and nanofluid modeling have strengthened my analytical and research capabilities. In addition, I possess experience in student supervision, assessment preparation, academic mentoring, and the use of mathematical software such as MATLAB, Maple, and LaTeX, making me well-suited for effective teaching, research, and academic service.', 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'Enjoy watching football and playing Valley ball', 'Immediately', 'I am currently a final year PhD. Mathematics Candidate at University technology and applied science Navrongo.', 'Benjamin Apam', 'Quality Assurance', 'Head of quality assurance Bolgatanga technical university', 'Post Office Box 767 Upper East Region Ghana', '+233 24 629 8163', 'bapam@bolgatu.edu.gh'