(53, 'BTU-1F976D98', 10, 'Mr.', 'AKOLGO', 'MOHAMMED', 'zugah1985@gmail.com', '0545564594', 'AZANTILOW SHTS, BOX 30, SANDEMA', 'BALUNGU', 'NAAGA', 'Upper East', 'GHANAIAN', 'ISLAM', 'married', 'AKAYENG MARY', 'AZANTILOW SHTS, BUNG. 5, SANDEMA', 'AKOLGO LUCIAN NSOHBEHEMA- 22/10/2012\r\nMOHAMMED NAQEYAT NMALEBNA - 17/02/2020\r\nMOHAMMED QUDDUS AYINE   - 07/10/2023', NULL, 'GHA-715823546-7', '1985-04-04', 'male', 'Master\'s Degree (MPhil.)', 'CKT UNIVERSITY OF TECHNOLOGY AND APPLIED SCIENCES, NAVRONGO', 2, '1. Agbedemnab, P. A., Akolgo, M., &amp; Agebure, M. A. (2023). A New Image Watermarking Scheme \r\nUsing Genetic Algorithm and Residual Numbers with Discrete Wavelet Transform. Journal of \r\nInformation Security, 14(4), 422-436.\r\n\r\n2. Akolgo, M., Anari, A. A., Batowise, B. E., &amp; Agbedemnab, P. A. (2024). Design and implementation of \r\nan IOT-Based Safety and Energy efficient system. Asian Journal of Research in Computer \r\nScience, 17(6), 78-187.\r\n\r\n3. Baagyere, E. Y., Agbedemnab, P. A., Akolgo, M. &amp; Bayitaa, S. A. (2024). A Nested Digital \r\nWatermarking Scheme Using GARN with DWT. Journal of Computer Science, 20(10), 1214-\r\n1221. https://doi.org/10.3844/jcssp.2024.1214.1221', NULL, 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'READING ACADEMIC ARTICLES\r\nLISTENING TO MUSIC', '2 WEEKS', 'I AM CURRENTLY READING PHD. IN COMPUTER SCIENCE IN UNIVERSITY OF TECHNOLOGY AND APPLIED SCIENCES', 'Prof. Peter Awon-natemi Agbedemnab (PhD)', 'Associate Professor', 'Principal', 'Tumu College of Education, Tumu', '0208529740', 'pagbedemnab@cktutas.edu.gh', 'Agebure Moses A. (PhD)', 'Senior Lecturer', 'Head of Department (Computer Science)', 'University of Technology and Applied Sciences, Navrongo', '0244696764', 'hodcss@utas.edu.gh', 'Ayambire Nyaaba Patrick (PhD)', 'Senior Lecturer', 'Lecturer', 'University of Skills Training and Entrepreneurial Development, Kumasi\r\nP.O Box 1277, Kumasi, Ghana', '0246664861', NULL, 'BTU_1F976D98_cv_6a12fe2bcc9e06.62602245.pdf', 'admissi