(83, 'BTU-9B6A1221', 15, 'Mr.', 'Kyemogo', 'Benjamin Naabankale', 'benjaminkyemogo@gmail.com', '0240121316', 'Jirapa Senior High School, Post Office Box 7, Upper West Region-Ghana.', 'Jirapa', 'Lawra', 'Upper West', 'Ghanaian', 'Christian', 'married', 'Tuonfiribo Marciana', 'Sacred Heart Senior High School, P.O.Box 3, Nsoatra-Bono', 'Kyemog Emmanuel  - 24th November, 2009\r\nKyemogo Nicholas   - 1st  September, 2017\r\nKyemogo Bryan - 13th September, 2020', 'P001135805X', 'GHA-715458588-1', '1976-06-16', 'male', 'Master\'s Degree (MPhil.)', 'University of Business and Integrated Development Studies.', 11, 'Not applicable', 'My experiences directly relates to that of the functions performed by Assistant Registrars been  an administrative leaders responsible for implementing policies and supervising key academic and  Human Resource functions.\r\n The Assistant Registrar  would also be relevant for the following tasks:\r\n\r\n-Administrative Support , providing  assistance to the Registrar in all administrative, secretarial, and human resource management matters of the University .\r\n\r\n-Academic Operations , involving  in implementing academic policies and procedures, such as those related to student admissions, examinations, and academic records .\r\n\r\n-Supervision,  supervising staff within their assigned sections or faculties to ensure the smooth delivery of registry services.', 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'Listening to Music and watching  football as sources of intertainment', 'If given the opportunity to serve, i will assumed office immediately.', 'With a strong background in academic administration, record management  and student services, I am eager to contribute to the smooth and efficient functioning of the  Registry Department.\r\nAdditionally ,I have  Ten  years of experience working in a  similar academic setting, where I handled tasks such as:\r\n-Vigorous enrollment drive\r\n-Maintaining and updating student academic records\r\n-Processing course registrations, transcript requests, and verification letters\r\n-Assisting in the coordination of matriculation, examinations, and convocation ceremonies\r\n\r\n-Responding to inquiries from students, staff, and external bodies in a professional and timely manner', 'Lobnibe Jane Frances (Dr)', 'Senior Lecturer', 'Dean, School of Education and Life-long Learning ( SoELL )', 'University of Business and Integrated Development of Studies, \r\nSchool of Education and Life long Learning\r\nP. O. Box 64, Wa Upper West Region-Ghana', '0201278603/054092021', 'jlobnibe@gmail.com', 'Abdul Mumuni Ds Adams', 'Headmaster', 'Headmaster, Jirapa Senior High School', 'Jirapa Senior High School, P. O BOX 7, Jirapa -Upper West Region-Ghana', '0203218505', 'zokyiere8773@gmail.com', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BTU_9B6A1221_cv_6a157568ba97e4.89947462.pdf', 'BENJAMIN\'S LATEST CV.pdf', 'pending', NULL, '154.161.118.18', '2026-05-26 10:26:48', '2026-06-07 23:59:41', 'BTU_9B6A1221_photo_6a157568ba9833.75011360.jpg', 'Picture 1.JPG'),
