telecom industry in Ghana? Cogent Business &amp; Management, 10(1), 2184743.', 'As a dedicated academic and researcher with a PhD in Accounting and Finance, my career seamlessly integrates advanced teaching, rigorous data-driven research, and professional consultancy. I leverage this expertise to bridge theoretical frameworks with practical industry applications, particularly within corporate finance, financial reporting, and data modeling. By fostering critical thinking in the classroom and publishing impactful, methodology-focused research, I bring a comprehensive, multifaceted approach to this role. My unique background equips me to advance the institution\'s academic excellence, drive innovative research initiatives, and mentor the next generation of professionals.', 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'I enjoy many hobbies and interests when I am not at work. I like playing volleyball and training, people.', '2 Weeks', NULL, 'Dr David Kwashie Garr', 'Lecturer', 'Senior Lecturer', 'Presbyterian University College of Ghana', '0244 330 854', 'davegarr2023@yahoo.com', 'Dr George K.S. Akorfu', 'Lecturer', 'Senior Lecturer', 'Wisconsin International University College -Ghana, g', '0244 520 207, 0576 3', 'eorge.akorfu@wiuc-ghana.edu.gh', 'Dr Kingsley S. Tornyeva', 'Accountant', 'Head of Finance', 'Quality Life Assurance', '0243 677 359', 'tornyeva@yahoo.com', 'BTU_A8773753_cv_6a16dc45d9e917.89365678.pdf', 'Application Documents.pdf', 'pending', NULL, '154.161.61.94', '2026-05-27 11:57:57', '2026-06-07 23:59:41', 'BTU_A8773753_photo_6a16dc45d9e960.95463492.jpg', 'David-Awadzie.jpg'),
