(107, 'BTU-BA14D242', 8, 'Dr.', 'David', 'Awadzie', 'davidawadzie@gmail.com', '+233242724282', 'P.O. Box AT1135, Achimota Market- Accra, Ghana', 'Accra', 'Accra', 'Greater Accra', 'Ghanaian', 'Christian', 'married', 'Dora Ohenwaa Agyekum', 'P.O. Box AT1135, Achimota Market- Accra, Ghana', 'Keziah Tiwaa Awadzie	                                                      14/09/2006	19\r\n Daniella Darkoa Awadzie	                                              18/10/2010	15\r\n Ebenezer Kofi Awadzie	                                                      25/10/2013	12\r\n Klara Afi Awadzie 	                                                              17/11/2017	  8', 'N/a', 'GHA-002060998-4', '1976-03-08', 'male', 'PhD', 'Open Univesity Malaysia', 0, '•	Awadzie, D. M., Garr, D. K., Gordor, S. S., &amp; Mawudor, B. G. (2025). Evaluation of the effect of modern approaches to management and leadership styles for sustainable business performance: the mediating role of innovation in the banking sector of Ghana. African Journal of Economic and Management Studies, 1-17.\r\n\r\n•	Awadzie, D. M., Garr, D. K., Zotoo, I. K., &amp; Marfo, M. (2025). The Sustainability of Budget Deficit and Public Debt on Ghanaian Economic Growth: The Government Intertemporal Budget. Urban Governance. doi: https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ugj.2025.05.002\r\n\r\n•	Awadzie, D. M., Attah-Botchwey, E., &amp; Mawudor, B. G. (2025). Determinants of the exchange rate threshold effect on economic growth. Evidence from Ghana. African Journal of Economic and Management Studies, 16(1), 47-60. https://doi.org/10.1108/AJEMS-10-2023-0383.\r\n\r\n•	Welbeck, D. N. O., Amponsah-Bediako, K., Asamoah, E. S., Quayson, A., &amp; Awadzie, D. M. (2025). Does Thought Leadership Enhance Managerial Performance? Mediating Role of Social Skills and Moderating the Role of Gender. Acta Universitatis Bohemiae Meridionalis, 28(1), 14-33.\r\n\r\n•	Awadzie, D. M., Garr, D. K., Attah-Botchwey, E., Koduah Sarpong, K., &amp; Marfo, M. (2023). Does corporate social responsibility promote the financial performance of the telecom industry in Ghana? Cogent Business &amp; Management, 10(1), 2184743.', 'As a dedicated academic and researcher with a PhD in Accounting and Finance, my career seamlessly integrates advanced teaching, rigorous data-driven research, and professional consultancy. I leverage this expertise to bridge theoretical frameworks with practical industry applications, particularly within corporate finance, financial reporting, and data modeling. By fostering critical thinking in the classroom and publishing impactful, methodology-focused research, I bring a comprehensive, multifaceted approach to this role. My unique background equips me to advance the institution\'s academic excellence, drive innovative research initiatives, and mentor the next generation of professionals.', 'no', 'no', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'I enjoy many hobbies and interests when I am not at work. I like playing volleyball and training, people.', NULL, NULL, 'Dr David Garr (PhD)', 'Lecturer', 'Senior Lecturer', 'Presbyterian University College of Ghana', '0244 330 854', 'davegarr2023@yahoo.com', 'Dr George K.S. Akorfu (PhD)', 'Lecturer', 'Senior Lecturer', 'Wisconsin International University College -Ghana', '0244 520 207, 0576 3', 'george.akorfu@wiuc-ghana.edu.gh', 'Dr Kingsley S. Tornyeva', 'Accountant', 'Head of Finance', 'Quality Life Assurance', '0243 677 359', 'tornyeva@yahoo.com', 'BTU_BA14D242_cv_6a16e0c65fb391.33138985.pdf', 'Application Documents.pdf', 'pending', NULL, '154.161.61.94', '2026-05-27 12:17:10', '2026-06-07 23:59:41', 'BTU_BA14D242_photo_6a16e0c65fb3d7.95532895.jpg', 'David-Awadzie.jpg'),
