(109, 'BTU-874E35C7', 16, 'Mr.', 'Sandow', 'Gilbert', 'Princegilbert2021@gmail.com', '+233203252884', 'Yagaba Senior High Technical School \r\nPost Office Box 13\r\nMamprugu Moaduri District \r\nNorth East Region', 'Walewale', 'Walewale', 'North East', 'Ghanaian', 'North East', 'married', 'Garisheba Priscilla Wuntimah', 'Arigu AG church, Box 13, Arigu-walewale, North East Region', 'Bariyona Janice Nasara \r\n22nd October, 2020', 'P0017255465', 'GHA-714479107-6', '1992-08-14', 'male', 'Master\'s Degree (MPhil.)', 'University of Cape Coast', 7, NULL, 'I am yet to publish two papers i have teased out of my thesis however the knowledge acquired through this Mphil programme in terms of research methodology and content mastery would be useful for the position l applied for.', 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, '1. I practice creative writing. \r\n2. Learning to sing and listen to gospel songs.\r\n3. Reading books. \r\n4. Walking \r\n5. Playing ludo', '2 weeks', 'I am endowed with excellent communication skills in teaching and learning environment; experience in a multi-cultural environment; multi-disciplinary background in communication skills, phonology, grammar, and sociolinguistics. A strong background in research methodology, academic writing (proposal writing), and psychology which would be helpful in the position applied.', 'Prof.Joseph Benjamin Archibald Afful', 'Lecturing', 'Post Graduate Students&#039; coordinator', 'Department of English \r\nFaculty of Arts \r\nUniversity of Cape Coast, Main Campus \r\nPMB, University post office \r\nCape Coast, Ghana.', '0245251989', 'Jafful@ucc.edu.gh', 'Prof. Moussa Traore', 'Lecturing', 'Head of Department of English', 'Department of English \r\nFaculty of Arts \r\nUniversity of Cape Coast, Main Campus \r\nPMB, University post office \r\nCape Coast, Ghana', '0208141667', 'Mtraore@ucc.edu.gh', 'Yussif Abdul-Aziz', 'Teaching', 'Headmaster', 'Nakpaduri Business Senior High School \r\nPost Office Box 5\r\nNakpaduri \r\nNorth East Reg