experience, and hands-on professional exposure positions me well to contribute meaningfully to teaching, research, and extension activities within the Agricultural Engineering Department, especially in the field of Irrigation Technology Engineering.', 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'Reading, watching football and history documentaries.', '1 month', 'N/A', 'Mr. Festus Barfi Fofie', 'Development worker', 'Program Director, Water Sanitation and Hygiene', 'Catholic Relief Services, Tamale.', '+233546661797', 'festus.fofie@crs.org', 'Mr. Edward Akunyagra', 'Development worker', 'Program Director, Agriculture Livelihood and Landscapes', 'Catholic Relief Services, Tamale.', '+233548992869', 'edward.akunyagra@crs.org', 'Rev. Prof Saa Dittoh', 'Professor', 'Adjunct Professor', 'West African Centre of Excellence for Water, Irrigation and Sustainable Agriculture (WACWISA), Nyankpala.', '+233244296612', 'saaditt@gmail.com', 'BTU_99F49FC1_cv_6a1726aee9d4f4.76710028.pdf', 'Emmanuel Ali Narimah_CV.pdf', 'pending', NULL, '154.161.49.79', '2026-05-27 17:15:26', '2026-06-07 23:59:41', 'BTU_99F49FC1_photo_6a1726aee9d538.18435679.jpg', 'passport.jpg'),
