(129, 'BTU-9F53EA08', 6, 'Ms.', 'Zangina', 'Emmanuella', 'zanginaemmanuella@gmail.com', '+233 593279723', NULL, 'Bolgatanga', NULL, 'Upper East', 'Ghanaian', 'Christianity', 'single', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GHA-722979761-0', '2000-12-24', 'female', 'Master\'s Degree (Other)', 'KWAME NKRUMAH UNIVERSITY OF SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY', 5, NULL, 'My academic background, teaching experience, research involvement and professional practice are highly relevant to the position of Lecturer in the Department of Building Technology. I hold a Master\'s degree in Construction Management and a First-Class Bachelor’s degree in Quantity Surveying and Construction Economics from KNUST. \r\nI have experienced teaching and mentoring students from your University during my time as a part-time instructor and a teaching and research assistant where I assisted in lecturing and assessing students in courses related to Construction Technology, Estimation, Measurement and Project Planning. \r\nProfessionally, I have gained practical experience in quantity surveying, contract documentation, project planning and site administration. I have also participated in research activities and a donor-funded research project on sustainable building materials. These experiences have equipped me with the academic, teaching, research and industry-oriented skills required to teach and mentor students in the department.', 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'Journaling and listening to music.', '2 weeks', NULL, 'Surv. Prof. Callistus Tengan', 'Lecturer', 'Associate Professor', 'Bolgatanga Technical University,\r\nBolgatanga,\r\nGhana.', '0241414463', 'tengan@bolgatu.edu.gh', 'Surv. Prof. Gabriel Nani', 'Lecturer', 'Associate Professor', 'Kwame Nkrumah University of Science and Technology,\r\nKumasi,\r\nGhana.', '0243625066', 'gnani.cap@knust.edu.gh', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BTU_9F53EA08_cv_6a18040ebd4960.68109004.pdf', 'EMMANUELLA ZANGINA - CV.pdf', 'pending', NULL, '154.161.237.95', '2026-05-28 08:59:58