ion Technologies and\r\nHuman Development.', 'My teaching, research, and professional experience are highly relevant to the position. I hold a PhD and a Master\'s degree in Information Systems from Cairo University. My teaching experience includes courses in programming, database systems, information systems, data analysis, and related computing disciplines. My research focuses on digital transformation, e-government, artificial intelligence applications, decision support systems, and data analytics, with several publications in reputable academic journals.\r\n\r\nIn addition, I have practical experience in data analysis, database management, enterprise architecture, and digital transformation initiatives. This combination of academic, research, and industry experience enables me to effectively teach undergraduate and postgraduate students, supervise research projects, and contribute to the academic and research objectives of the institution.', 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'football ,swimming', 'Within one month of notification, subject to visa and travel arrangements', NULL, 'Ehab Hasaean', 'Prof', 'Head of information systems Department   Faculty of Computers and Information  Cairo University', 'Cairo, egypt', '00201151160773', 'e.ezat@fci-cu.edu.eg', 'Hatem Elkadi', 'Prof', 'Professor of information systems Department and my supervisor in master and PhD. Faculty of Computer', 'Cairo, egypt', '+20 10 01401012', 'hkadi@fci-cu.edu.eg', 'Neamat El Tazi', 'Prof', 'Professor of information systems Department and my supervisor in master and PhD. Faculty of Computer', 'Cairo, egypt', '+20 11 10241494', 'n.eltazi@fci-cu.edu.eg', 'BTU_707800A0_cv_6a1d7e9247d1f4.69748422.pdf', '???? ????? ??????? ???????.pdf', 'pending', NULL, '209.198.151.202', '2026-06-01 12:44:02', '2026-06-07 23:59:41', 'BTU_707800A0_photo_6a1d7e9247d252.11207868.jpg', 'passport.jpg'),
