(294, 'BTU-7512E0C9', 14, 'Mrs.', 'ADOMBIRE', 'DORCAS', 'adombiredorcas97@gmail.com', '+233 240478558', NULL, 'Bolgatanga', 'Bongo', 'Upper East', 'Ghanaian', 'Christian', 'married', 'NDOOR PATRICK', 'Bolgatanga- Bongo', 'Precious Lael Ndoor 24/04/2024', NULL, 'GHA- 722825148-3', '1997-07-03', 'female', 'WASSCE/SSSCE', 'Bongo Senior High', 3, NULL, 'My research on auditing deepened my understanding of financial systems and audit processes, which directly supports the accounting and reporting responsibilities required for this role within an academic institution.', 'yes', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'Writing Financial literature \r\nWriting Novels\r\nListening to current affairs', '2 weeks', 'I am a dedicated and detail-oriented accounting professional with hands-on experience in financial reporting, budget analysis, and external audit support etc. I hold a strong academic background, including dissertation-level research in auditing, and have demonstrated the ability to work accurately under pressure and meet financial deadlines consistently.\r\nI am particularly drawn to Bolgatanga Technical University because I believe my skills in financial management, combined with my understanding of academic institutional environments, position me to contribute meaningfully to the university\'s financial operations and long-term goals.\r\nI am highly adaptable, a quick learner, and committed to upholding the highest standards of integrity and professionalism in every financial responsibility entrusted to me.', 'Clement Boakye', 'Accountant', 'Accountant', 'Accra- Ghana', '0542550846', NULL, 'Patrick Ndoor', 'Teacher', 'Teacher', NULL, '0249713708', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BTU_7512E0C9_cv_6a20318f7ec259.11194025.pdf', 'CV- DORCAS ADOMBIRE.pdf', 'pending', NULL, '154.161.16.113', '2026-06-03 13:52:15', '2026-06-07 23:59:41', 'BTU_7512E0C9_photo_6a20318f7ec2a3.09575063.jpg', '46216.jpg'),
