, environmental sustainability and construction maintenance. The mining discipline connects and integrates all these areas that i have both practical experience and theoretical knowledge', 'no', 'no', NULL, 'no', NULL, 'TRAVELLING AND SIGHT SEEING', '2 WEEKS', NULL, 'Dr. Daniel Jato Espino', 'Senior Lecturer(Civil)', 'Senior Researcher', 'Valencia International University, Spain', '+34680209260', 'Djato@universidadviu.com', 'Jorge Hernandez Rodriguez (Prof.)', 'Academics', 'Head of Studies (Civil Eng. Dept.)', 'University of Cantabria (Spain)', '+34680546512', 'Jorge.rodriguez@unican.es', 'Fausta Ganaa (Mrs)', 'Administrator', 'Public Relations Officer', 'Accra Technical University', '+233548032968', 'fkganaa@atu.edu.gh', 'BTU_7E0B9C1D_cv_6a26f6b8f3c6e1.16840153.pdf', 'Yiwo CV_P.update.pdf', 'pending', NULL, '154.161.170.45', '2026-06-08 17:07:05', '2026-06-08 17:07:05', 'BTU_7E0B9C1D_photo_6a26f6b8f3c748.13743078.jpeg', 'Passport photo_Dr. Yiwo.jpeg'),
