(170, 87, 'Sept 2019', 'Aug 2017', 'Ghana broadcasting corporation, URA radio Bolga', 'Bolga', 'Account office assistant', 'Debtors and creditor records keeping\r\nKeeping Cash book records\r\nIssuing receipts and daily banking of cash/cheques\r\nIn charge of records in the Assets register\r\nPayment of VAT, NHIL&amp;Getfund\r\nWriting of PV’S\r\nUpdating of ledgers', '', 'On attachment', 1),
