(203, 101, '1ST FEBRUA', NULL, 'BOLGATANGA TECHNICAL INSTITUTE', 'P.O.BOX 295', 'SENIOR TUTOR', 'CLASSROOM TEACHER,FORM MASTER AND SUBJECT TAUGHT: PRACTICALS,DESIGN AND DRAWING,PRINCIPLES OF PAINTING AND DECORATING,ART PROCESS.\r\nMY RESPONSIBILITIES IS TO BRING THE BEST IN MY STUDENTS AND ALSO GUIDE THEM INTO THE RIGHT PATH IN FUTURE.', 'full-time', NULL, 0),
