(215, 109, 'September,', NULL, 'Yagaba Senior High Technical School', 'Yagaba Senior High Technical School, Box 13, Mamprugu Moaduri District, North East Region', 'Teacher- Head of Languages Department', '1. Assign teachers in my department to various classes. \r\n2. Vet scheme of work and learning plans design for teaching\r\n3. Supervise both teachers and students under my jurisdiction to ensure effective teaching and learning. \r\n4. Attend academic board meetings \r\n5. Design a programme outline for the department in every semester.\r\n6. coordinate inter-school debate, drama, quizzes, \r\n7. I teach English Language', 'full-time', NULL, 0),
