(240, 118, 'FEB 2023', NULL, 'BOLGATANGA TECHNICAL UNIVERSITY', 'BOLGATANGA', 'PART SECURITY', 'Monitoring Access Points: Checking windows, doors, and gates to ensure they are securely locked and functioning properly.\r\nVerifying Identity: Checking IDs, badges, or visitor logs to ensure only authorized personnel enter the facility.\r\nManaging Deliveries: Inspecting incoming and outgoing vehicles or packages to prevent theft or contraband entry.\r\nAssisting Visitors: Directing guests, answering basic questions, and ensuring they follow onsite safety protocols.\r\nDaily Logs: Maintaining an accurate written or digital record of daily activities, observations, and unusual occurrences.\r\nIncident Reports: Writing detailed, objective reports when a crime, accident, or policy violation occurs, which may be used by management or law enforcement.', 'full-time', NULL, 0),
