(316, 161, 'Mar, 2026', NULL, 'Bolgatanga Technical University', 'Bolgatanga Upper East Region', 'Assistant Lecturer', 'At Bolgatanga Technical University, I am actively involved in key academic responsibilities that support effective teaching and student assessment. My duties include setting and marking assignments and examination questions, invigilating examinations, and ensuring the proper submission of marked scripts and results in line with institutional requirements.\r\nIn addition, I contribute to teaching and practical instruction in hardware and software systems, system analysis and design, and networking and cabling, providing students with both theoretical understanding and hands-on technical skills aligned with industry practice.', 'full-time', NULL, 0),
(317, 161, 'Jun, 2025', NULL, 'Regentropfen University Collage Kansoe', 'Bolgatanga Upper East Region', 'Assistant Lecturer', 'At Regentropfen University College, I undertake a range of academic and administrative responsibilities that contribute to effective teaching, assessment, and student development.\r\nMy teaching duties include delivering courses such as Introduction to Artificial Intelligence and Expert Systems, as well as Legal and Ethical Issues in Computer Science. I also support student learning through the preparation, setting, and marking of assignments and examination questions.\r\nIn addition, I participate in the invigilation of examinations and ensure the accurate and timely submission of marked scripts and results in accordance with institutional requirements.\r\nFurthermore, I provide academic counselling to students to support their academic progress and personal development.', 'full-time', NULL, 1),
