(363, 177, 'Jan 2025', 'Dec 2025', 'LMI - Holdings', 'Tema Industrial Area - Community 25', 'Production Manager', '•	Led end-to-end plant operations, delivering 300m³/day with 95–98% on-time performance across key projects (Sienna Services, John Murphy – Freezones &amp; Dawa, Land Investments)\r\n•	Ensured compliance with mix designs and quality standards, improving consistency and reducing quality deviations by 20–30%\r\n•	Achieved 95% plant uptime, reducing breakdown frequency by 20–25% through effective maintenance\r\n•	Improved cost efficiency, reducing material wastage by 10–20% and optimizing inventory management\r\n•	Strengthened reconciliations, internal controls, and reporting, improving data accuracy and audit compliance by 95%', 'full-time', 'Better Opportunity', 0),
