(393, 187, 'November, ', '2013', 'College of Health, Nalerigu', 'P. O. Box 10, Nalerigu-NER', 'Snr Health Tutor/Snr Nutrition Officer', '1.	Deliver lectures and practical instruction in:\r\na.	Basic Nutrition\r\nb.	Nutrition Screening and Assessment, \r\nc.	Nutrition Communication and Report Writing Skills\r\nd.	Research Methods\r\ne.	Nutritional Problems and Interventional Strategies.\r\n\r\n2.	Lead practical on anthropometric measurement and formula feed preparation\r\n3.	Supervise research projects and provide academic mentorship.\r\n4.	Lead curriculum planning, instructional development, student assessment, and academic reporting.', '', 'National service period was over', 0),
