(398, 188, 'January 20', NULL, 'Docmorrison Pharmacy Limited', 'P. O. Box DC 68, Dansoman Community', 'Finance Manager', '*As a team lead for finance, I supervised and ensured our daily weekly, monthly and annual targets are achieved.\r\n*Prepared purchasing orders to ensure timely availability of pharmacy inventory.\r\n*Performed bookkeeping activities to maintain accurate financial records.\r\n*Prepared asset register.\r\n*Ensured accurate submission of taxes and SSNIT records.\r\n*Completed payroll accounting to ensure timely employee compensation.', 'full-time', NULL, 0),
