(424, 202, '2011', NULL, 'West African Network for Peace Building', 'Accra, Greatet Accra Region', 'Assistant Program Manager', '•	Coordinated project timelines and deliverables, enhancing team collaboration and communication across departments.\r\n•	Developed strategic plans for program implementation, aligning resources with organizational objectives and goals.\r\n•	Facilitated stakeholder meetings to gather requirements and feedback, fostering a collaborative project environment.\r\n•	Planned and conducted strategic meetings for effective project delivery\r\n•	Trained stakeholders on peace building techniques and conflict early warning signs\r\n•	Assisted in conducting mediation for various communities\r\n•	Conducted effective monitoring and evaluation and drafted project reports\r\n•	Monitored elections in selected West African countries', 'full-time', NULL, 3),
