(476, 229, 'January 20', 'May 2025', 'Zeus Atlas Limited', 'No. 14 Mensah Anteh Street, Ashongman Estates', 'Facilitator', 'Led delivery of Essential IT Skills sessions at multiple training Centre’s, adapting content to participant skill levels and Centre resources.\r\n\r\nCollaborated with the Lead Facilitator to design and refine slide decks, manuals, and hands on exercises for each topic.\r\n\r\nExecuted all tasks required for successful module implementation, including lesson planning, participant assessment, and session facilitation.\r\n\r\nMonitored performance against Key Performance Indicators provided by the Lead Facilitator and implemented corrective actions when needed.\r\n\r\nEnsured compliance with programme guidelines and Ghanaian data protection rules; secured and processed participant data per Company instructions.\r\n\r\nCoordinated logistics and requested company approved tools and reimbursements in advance.', 'full-time', 'Relocated to the North', 0),
(477, 229, 'January 20', NULL, 'Indigin Group', 'Tema Community 25 Dahwenya.', 'IT Officer/Social Media Executive', 'Maintained IT infrastructure such as servers, networks, and hardware/software. \r\n\r\nEnsured systems secured and updated. \r\n\r\nTroubleshoot and resolve technical issues within the organization. \r\n\r\nImplemented and optimize IT solutions and tools. \r\n\r\nCollaborated cross-functionally with developers, and stakeholders to meet diverse project requirements. \r\n\r\nMaintained thorough documentation of development processes and adhering to industry best practices. \r\n\r\nManaged and grow the company’s social media profiles and presence. \r\n\r\nDeveloped and executed comprehensive social media strategies aligned with organizational goals. \r\n\r\nCreated, curate, and managed content for social media platforms. \r\n\r\nCollaborated with marketing team to create compelling content for blogs, social media, and websites. \r\n\r\nTracked content performance using analytics tools and refine strategies for improvement. \r\n\r\nEnsured search engine optimization of content for enhanced visibility and audience reach. \r\n\r\nGenerated regular reports on social media performance and IT system health.', 'full-time', NULL, 1),
(478, 230, 'April, 202', NULL, 'Judicial Service of Ghana', 'Box BL 6', 'Deputy Chief Registrar/Cashier', '1. Preparation of bank reconciliation statement and summary of the Court.\r\n\r\n2. Maintain bookkeeping of the Court.\r\n\r\n3. Assist in updating office asset register and tagging of the court assets\r\n\r\n4. Ensures compliance with established internal control procedures by examining records, reports, operating practices, and documentations\r\n\r\n5. Support the reviewing of invoices, payments, vouchers and receipts\r\nProcess and payment of court compensations.', 'full-time', NULL, 0),
