(487, 237, 'September ', NULL, 'Regentropfen University College', 'RUC Private Mail Bag, Upper East Region. Kansoe-Namoo', 'Lecturer', 'As a Lecturer at Regentropfen University College since September 2023, I teach courses including Computer Organization and Architecture, Systems Analysis and Design, Data Structures and Algorithm Design, Research Methods in Computing, IT Project Management, IT Entrepreneurship, Database Management Systems, and Python for Data Analysis. My responsibilities include delivering lectures and practical sessions, preparing course materials, assessing students, supervising research projects, mentoring students, and contributing to curriculum development and academic quality assurance. \r\n\r\nSince March 2024, I have also served as a Part-Time Assistant Lecturer at Bolgatanga Technical University, where I teach Introduction to Digital Logic, Guided Media, Routing and Switching Technologies, Fundamentals of Data Communication, Computer Hardware and Software Technologies, Fundamentals of Computer Networks, and Network Architecture, while supporting student learning through lectures, practical instruction, and assessments. \r\n\r\nAdditionally, I serve as Assistant Examination Officer at Regentropfen University College, where I coordinate examination planning and scheduling, support examination administration and invigilation, manage student examination records, address examination malpractice issues, and ensure the confidentiality and security of examination materials and records.', 'full-time', NULL, 0),
