(590, 280, 'April 2025', NULL, 'Central University', 'Dawhenya, Ghana', 'Adjunct Lecturer', '1. Teach Soil and Rock Mechanics to Level 200 undergraduate students and Foundation \r\nEngineering to Level 300 students.  \r\n2. Prepare and deliver lectures, tutorials, and assessment materials in line with university \r\nacademic standards.  \r\n3. Simplify complex geotechnical engineering concepts through practical examples and \r\ninteractive learning approaches.  \r\n4. Support students in developing analytical and problem-solving skills relevant to civil and \r\nenvironmental engineering applications.  \r\n5. Contribute to academic mentoring and student engagement to enhance learning outcomes \r\nand professional readiness.', 'full-time', NULL, 0),
