(619, 297, '2021', 'Aug 2017', 'Access bank plc', 'Bolga Branch', 'Cashier/Relationship officer', 'Duties Assigned\r\nManaging customers portfolio \r\nHandling Credit facilities \r\nProcessing of outwards transfer\r\nCustomer acquisition\r\nCustomer Relationship management\r\nCross selling the bank product to customers\r\nI have worked as an RO with access bank Bolga branch since 2025 July to date. As a relationship Officer, I have gained in deep knowledge on the above and more.\r\n\r\nDuties Assigned\r\nProcessing of deposits and withdraw\r\nProcessing of remittances\r\nProcessing of expenses\r\nI have worked as a cashier four years with access bank, Bolga Branch', '', 'Attachment it was', 0),
(620, 297, '2019', 'May 2016', 'Ghana Broadcasting corporation, URA radio Bolga', 'URA radio Bolga NSS', 'Office assistant', 'Duties Assigned\r\nDebtors and creditor records keeping\r\nKeeping Cash book records\r\nIssuing receipts and daily banking of cash/cheques\r\nIn charge of records in the Assets register\r\nPayment of VAT, NHIL&amp;Getfund\r\nWriting of PV’S\r\nUpdating of ledgers\r\nOrganization: Kassena Nankana Municipal Assembly- Navrongo\r\nDepartment:  Finance Office\r\nJob Title:  Office Assistant (Students Second Semester Attachment)\r\nDuties Assigned\r\nWriting of Payment Vouchers (PV’S)\r\nReconciling Cash Book with Bank Statement\r\nDocument Filing \r\nReceiving and Dispatching of Letters', 'full-time', 'Left to further my education', 1),
(621, 297, 'June 2017', NULL, 'UDS Navrongo', 'Upper East', 'Office Assistant', 'Duties Assigned\r\nBank Reconciliation using excel\r\nRecording of Transaction in Goods Received Book\r\nIssuing of Receipts using receipts book\r\nPreparation of Cash Book using excel\r\nPhysical Inventory Counting using inventory control ledger', 'full-time', NULL, 2),
