(629, 302, '2005 TO DA', NULL, 'Zorkor Senior High School', 'P. O. Box 56 Bongo', 'SUBJECT TEACHER', '1.	LESSON PLANNING AND RESOURCE DEVELOPMENT \r\n2.	INSTRUCTION AND LESSON DEVIVERY\r\n3.	CLASSROOM MANAGEMENT \r\n4.	STUDENT ASSESSMENT AND FEEDBACK\r\n5.	MENTORSHIP AND STUDENT DEVELOPMENT \r\n6.	INVIGilATION FOR WASSCE EXAMS \r\n7.	EXAMINER FOR BOTH WASSCE AND BECE', 'full-time', NULL, 0),
